Will be able to add columns, named, add tasks, click and drag move tasks between columns
delete tasks, edit tasks, sort columns,
React Typescript, Tailwind CSS, and DND kit(drag and drop kit)
'npm create vite' #Will create a vite project name=KanBan, React, Typescript + SWC,
'cd kanban' #change directory to newly created vite project
npm i #install dependencies
npm install @dnd-kit/core @dnd-kit/sortable #will install drag and drop dependanSeans
next we are going to add tailwindCSS
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer #will install tailwindCSS
npx tailwindcss init -p #will initialize tailwindCSS, create 2 config files
Next we will need to replace the tailwindcss 'tailwind.config.js' file with the following as per below:
https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation
content: ["./index.html", "./src/**/*.{html,js,ts,jsx,tsx}"], #will enable tailwind on JS6, TS6, TS, and JS
Next we will create a theme, with colours. in the 'tailwind.config.js'
Next we will purge the 'index.css'
npm install tailwind-merge #will install tailwind-merge

npm run dev #starts development server
